---
title: Speedy Korean BBQ Tofu Tacos with Pear & Carrot Slaw
description: Little on time and big on flavour, these simple tacos have sweet and salty glazed tofu, crunchy pear slaw and garlic aioli all wrapped up in a warm tortilla. Now that's a lot of good things to smile about!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/korean-tofu-tacos-0e91d68a.jpg
